rmcp crate chosen for MCP server implementation: built-in JSON-RPC handling, stdio transport, tool/resource/prompt support, subscription support. Benefits: standards-compliant, reduced boilerplate, active development. Native Rust implementation superior to Python equivalent. This is ADR-009.